org.itsnat.comp.button.toggle

Interface ItsNatFreeRadioButtonLabel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatButton, ItsNatButtonLabel, ItsNatButtonRadio, ItsNatButtonToggle, ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatFreeButtonToggle, ItsNatFreeComponent, ItsNatFreeRadioButton, ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatFreeRadioButtonLabel
extends ItsNatFreeRadioButton, ItsNatButtonLabel
    Is the interface of the default implementation of free radio buttons. This component version has a label.

    ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.
